  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 20th Level, your technique is so overwhelmingly powerful that your enemies speak of you as if you are a force of nature. </p><p>Something that is unavoidable and if encountered, can only be weathered. </p><p>When you would cast a Taijutsu that requires you to make no more than 1 attack, you may spend 4 martial die, granting it the Nin-Tai keyword. </p><p>Taijutsu with the Nin-Tai keyword scores a critical hit on a D20 roll of a 10 or better. </p><p>Once you use this feature, you must spend 4 martial die at the beginning of one of your turns to recharge this feature.</p>",
